==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Isochronize
<hw>I*soch"ro*nize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>-nized</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. &
vb. n.</pos> <conjf>-nizing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[See
<er>Isochronous</er>.]</ety> <def>To make, or tend to make (the motion
of a moving body), uniform in rate of rotation, or in frequency of
vibration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

